## Development Commands

### Backend (Strapi)
```bash
cd backend
npm install                        # Install dependencies
npm run develop                    # Start Strapi in dev mode (:1337)
npm run build                      # Build Strapi admin
npm run start                      # Start Strapi in production mode
npm run strapi generate            # Generate content types, APIs, etc.
```

### Frontend (Astro)
```bash
cd frontend
npm install                        # Install dependencies
